<quantity box="[396,576,1605,1631]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.6465" metricValueMax="2.842" metricValueMin="2.451" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" unit="m" value="2.6465" valueMax="2.842" valueMin="2.451">2,451–2,842 m</quantity>
. Near to hydrothermal vents.
</paragraph>
